episodes.title: Scars
episodes.plot: The women and staff of Wentworth are reeling in the aftermath of Bea Smith's murder in a new era for the prison. While Vera has to set up a member of staff to take the heat away from herself.

episodes.title: The Bitch Is Back
episodes.plot: Franky's trapped by her past, Vera takes desperate measures to foil Ferguson's self defence plea, Liz starts to regret her decision to testify against Sonia.

episodes.title: Nothing But the Truth
episodes.plot: Liz goes to Court to give her statement against Sonia and her defence is torn to shreds by Sonia's defence team and Franky continues her mission to find Mike's killer.

episodes.title: Loose Ends
episodes.plot: While Liz languishes back in Wentworth waiting for Don to come to her rescue, Sonia is a free woman, and Franky plans her escape.

episodes.title: Belly of the Beast
episodes.plot: Franky's escape plan could have fatal consequences and Liz is forced to take drastic measures to protect herself.

episodes.title: Happy Birthday, Vera
episodes.plot: The women become frustrated with the Top Dog's lack of action against Lucy, and Vera receives a birthday present she will never forget.

episodes.title: The Pact
episodes.plot: Will tries to set up a trap to end the drug supply in the prison with help from Kaz and Allie. While Doreen receives a happy ending when she gets her parole.

episodes.title: Think Inside the Box
episodes.plot: Franky's escape plan derails her relationship with Bridget, Sonia unleashes on Liz, and Will makes a shocking discovery.

episodes.title: Snakehead
episodes.plot: Will sets out to expose Jake, forcing Vera to make a choice; Franky engages help from the outside, while the net tightens around Liz.

episodes.title: Mere Anarchy
episodes.plot: Franky faces danger from an unexpected source, Ferguson pulls strings to sideline Vera, and Liz goes to extreme lengths to try to get a confession from Sonia.

episodes.title: Coup de Grace
episodes.plot: Ferguson delivers Vera her coup de grace, unleashing unforeseen consequences; Franky's escape plans are waylaid when Kaz persuades her to join forces to bring down the Freak.

episodes.title: Hell Bent
episodes.plot: Franky and Allie put their escape plan into action, Liz takes desperate measures to protect herself, and Ferguson suspects she's living on borrowed time.
